		<hr size="1">Yes you can raise your Int later and end up with the same amount of mana. No, you are not given mana at level up depending on your int amount. You could be nekkid til lvl 40, put on gear to get your int to 200, and still have the same amount of mana as somebody who has had 200 int since lvl 1.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=89593" target="_blank">Yeldare</a>, 49 Wizard<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=99217" target="_blank">Sormi</a>, 36 Warrior<br>Both on the Luclin server.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
